		<div class="title">
			<h4><a rel="nofollow" id="comment_link_65393289" name="comment_link_65393289" href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23698323&amp;cid=65393289" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(65393289)" >Such corporate bullshit</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_65393289" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 65393289); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>5</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~flibbidyfloo">flibbidyfloo</a>  <span class="uid"><a rel="nofollow" href="//slashdot.org/~flibbidyfloo">( 451053 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
